author: Inside Edition
description: Matthew Perry's grieving parents wrote heartfelt letters made public Wednesday accusing Dr. Salvador Plasencia of being "among the most culpable of all" of the people who supplied drugs to Perry. The letters came as Dr. Plasencia pled guilty to four counts of distributing 20 vials of ketamine for $55,000. Perry was found dead in his hot tub in October 2023. He became addicted to ketamine, which he used to treat his depression.
title: Matthew Perry's Parents Condemn Doctor

author: Inside Edition
description: Thursday marks one year since the assassination of United Healthcare CEO Brian Thompson on a New York City street. Luigi Mangione was arrested in Pennsylvania five days later and brought to New York City to face trial. Thompson was a husband and father of two teenaged sons. The family is keeping a low profile and scrubbed their social media. Thompson, 50, had no bodyguard, but security experts in high profile business executives now have teams of armed personnel protecting them.
title: After UHC CEO Assassination, Executives Opt For Security Teams

author: Inside Edition
description: President Donald Trump had two large band-aids on the back of his right hand at Tuesday's cabinet meeting and again later at an event in the Oval Office. It's the same hand that has been seen bruised and covered with makeup. There has not been a comment from the White House about the band-aids and the president laughed off concerns about his health. Trump appeared to fall asleep as administration officials were filling him in on their accomplishments.
title: President Trump's Bruised Hand Covered With Band-Aids

author: Inside Edition
description: Tis the season to be jolly, unless you're walking through Brussels and get offended by this nativity scene. An artist has been getting  a lot of blowback for her Nativity scene, which features faceless statues. Instead, she used balls of cloth to create heads for the human-shaped figures. Inside Edition Digital’s Mara Montalbano has more.
title: Faceless Nativity Statues Cause Controversy In Brussels
